<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-4ED99740-E293-4E98-9B86-3959346620E1" version="1" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-4ED99740-E293-4E98-9B86-3959346620E1" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">02 How to install the ink refill unit</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-0E3E2CA2-5349-4FAF-80F5-347AA9765351"><p class="- topic/p ">This document describes how to install the ink refill unit. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Dis-assembly</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-E46F8DDC-7D6F-40DC-9068-F1E3819FBFBF" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-1DBFF03A-0802-46EF-A302-C72A452F8725" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">The knife that cuts the ink bottle is uncovered when you remove the ink bottle. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_5319AAF504144C93A8D661E317AE9889" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_AAA0FC8490A547538C29E0A65ABF9B58" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Small screwdriver 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Flash light (No LED) 
</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves : 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-DB340B14-87E5-4FDB-8108-245D16C84FF1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="FIG_C24E6AAB222D49CEA1D3210A1A9A96E2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-379D3C51-14CA-472C-B79F-A7B1772709BA-low.png" id="IMAGE_C3F3FD752C894D3997FB8E159719DF00" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-379D3C51-14CA-472C-B79F-A7B1772709BA-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table id="GUID-BDB87D50-9E70-4086-AC9E-FA7970C76B0D" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Install the ink refill unit: 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Tilt the unit a little bit. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Place it in the 6 holes of the ink cabinet. 
</p></li></ol><note id="GUID-08637617-3536-4BAB-9BEA-4E5C9458C79F" type="note" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Make sure that the funnel of the ink refill unit is positioned in the hole of the ink tank. 
</p></note></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-C0BC1E7F-627E-4380-97A9-5DAEE3C85DA4" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-A97B7510-C7A4-4886-9DAB-A36F4AA3BBFA-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-A97B7510-C7A4-4886-9DAB-A36F4AA3BBFA-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the ink cabinet. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Check: Make sure that the funnel is in the hole of the cover of the ink tank. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-EB4EB563-2A8C-44A8-BF24-B1D6BD7FD5AD" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D040F432-604D-4BCB-AEA5-502184FAF93E-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D040F432-604D-4BCB-AEA5-502184FAF93E-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> First, mount the 2 screws loose, on the rear side of the refill unit. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-059010D9-21A2-408D-BB33-7BDC5AD243E4" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-9B585D1E-D724-45FA-8FE3-688C539D8D23-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-9B585D1E-D724-45FA-8FE3-688C539D8D23-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Mount the 2 screws on the front side of the refill unit. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-1E27DB9D-0897-4C1A-B7F9-33D66B338594" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D415F8D8-6D65-40C1-A45D-42A192AED314-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D415F8D8-6D65-40C1-A45D-42A192AED314-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Fasten the 2 screws on the back side of the refill unit. There will be a resistance felt as the funnel is pushed into the cover of the ink tank. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-6321C32C-1747-4DFC-A75A-58E906B056C2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-A2D44AB4-05C4-489D-A931-F635F3AF8F2B-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-A2D44AB4-05C4-489D-A931-F635F3AF8F2B-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Check:</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Check if the funnel is in the correct position. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If not, loosen all 4 bolts and repeat step 1-5. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-59CBC719-A14F-429F-BAC3-B86E5BE9FDA1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-2983D8A2-4B0A-4E0D-AE50-B34CCADB0746-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-2983D8A2-4B0A-4E0D-AE50-B34CCADB0746-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-88754200-5F2D-4745-8F0D-BF5E72C090A2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-F167F1A2-DDEE-4749-BF74-FCF8BD27A44D-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-F167F1A2-DDEE-4749-BF74-FCF8BD27A44D-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">In case a 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">new</b> ink refill unit is installed: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Do 
<xref keyref="SDS02-8-002" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-DB370C6E-BD29-4995-992D-AB565FDDBADD.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 02-8-002 Number of inserted cartridges current ink refill unit (C,M,Y or K) [Maintenance Counters]?>02-8-002 Number of inserted cartridges current ink refill unit (C,M,Y,K or W) [Maintenance Counters]</xref> and reset the value to 0. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-1CE85252-F6D3-4421-930B-8AE723FFB49C.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Dis-assembly</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
</task>